{{ill|Sashikuni Ōkami|lt=Sashikuni Ōkami|ja|刺国大神|en:draft|6=simple|7=User:Immanuelle/Sashikuni_Okami|8=fr|qq=draft|qq=draft}} (刺国大神) was a Japanese deity associated with {{ill|Susanoo|1=Susanoo-no-Mikoto|lt=Susanoo-no-Mikoto|en|qq=draft|qq=draft}} and the [[Izumo Province|Izumo Province]].<ref name="fountainhead" />{{rp|278}}<ref name=":0" />

